<!--


Design for command-line geeks but also fine for daily use.
Easy to access:
- CTRL (Z/X/C/J/L/V/B) for tmux user
- "g-hjkl" for vim user

[B] = backspace
[S] = shift
{E} = esc
[R] = enter
[C] = ctrl
[ ] = space
[X] = x + (up: SHIFT)
[Z] = z + (right: ESC)

 q   w   e   r   t   y   u  [B]
 a   s   d   f   g   i   o   p
[X]   c   v   b   h   j   k   l
[C] [Z]  v   b  [ ]  n   m  [R]


-->
